title: Run Run Superman FLAC
description:
Hello dear listener,

Here is for you, completely legal, a FLAC version of the originals of the CD Run Run Superman by Rinzo & The Hey Hey Panthers. The music is usable under the conditions of CC-BY as stated on the Jamendo-page. To support the artists there are several options, all listed on the official website, http://panthers.rinzo.nl/. We think it's really cool if you do support us in any way, but most of all, we think it would be really cool if our music ends up everywhere.

So, happy listening, and please comment back to us about our music!

LaPingvino, on behalve of Rinzo
